## Basics Workbook (Bar Chart) 

Objective: Analyse structured sales data to determine: 
- The representative with the highest total sales overall (for bonus allocation) 
- The representative with the highest sales amount in each region (for regional bonuses) 

Visual Features: 
- Sum of total sales per representative displayed 
- Regions differentiated by distinct colours and grouped visually 
- Clear labels for sales figures and representative names 

Technical Elements Practised: 
- Created calculated fields 
- Applied colour coding by region 
- Used labels for clarity 
- Adjusted formatting for readability

Purpose: First tableau project to explore basic features, practise interactivity and develop visual storytelling skills 
